han full-page layouts.\n*   **Beat the Median**:\n    *   *Tech*: Expert use of GPT-4o-mini vision capabilities mapping mock layouts to production-ready Tailwind.\n    *   *Design*: Split-pane IDE aesthetic with zero configuration.\n    *   *Impact*: Immediate utility for every frontend engineer.\n    *   *Quality*: Extremely high legibility in a 15-second demo video.\n\n### 3. Socratic.gg: AI Study Opponent\n*   **Description**: Upload a lecture slide or syllabus, and engage in a real-time, interactive, voice-driven debate with an AI tutor that dynamically visualizes your logical fallacies on a canvas as you speak.\n*   **Why It Matters**: True active recall happens through defense of concepts, not passive flashcards.\n*   **Track**: Education\n*   **Aha Moment**: Speak a thesis $\\rightarrow$ voice responds in real-time $\\rightarrow$ canvas updates with an interactive \"Logical Fallacy Mindmap\" showing gaps in your knowledge.\n*   **3-Day Scope Cut**: Web Speech API for native browser text-to-speech/speech-to-text; skip custom audio streaming pipelines.\n*   **Beat the Median**:\n    *   *Tech*: Merging real-time transcriptions with dynamic visual graph generation.\n    *   *Design*: Minimalist dark-mode canvas styled like a high-end brainstorming tool.\n    *   *Impact*: Upgrades rote memorization to high-agency critical thinking.\n    *   *Quality*: Highly interactive and visually engaging.\n\n### 4. SplitSecond: Visual Receipt Allocator\n*   **Description**: Snap a photo of a messy group receipt. The app parses items into interactive drag-and-drop cards; drag roommate/friend avatars onto items to instantly generate custom Venmo request links.\n*   **Why It Matters**: Eliminates the mental math and manual typing of splitting complicated bills.\n*   **Track**: Apps for Your Life\n*   **Aha Moment**: Drop a receipt image $\\rightarrow$ items become draggable cards $\\rightarrow$ drag friend avatar to item $\\rightarrow$ instant Venmo deep links generated.\n*   **3-Day Scope Cut**: Static Venmo deep link generation (URL scheme-based) with no actual banking API integration.\n*   **Beat the Median**:\n    *   *Tech*: Structured OCR parsing using vision models directly to stateful UI cards.\n    *   *Design*: Tactile, mobile-first, fluid drag-and-drop animations.\n    *   *Impact*: High utility for immediate, real-world social friction.\n    *   *Quality*: Clear, undeniable UX utility in a 10-second demo.\n\n### 5. OutOfOffice: Async Handoff Generator\n*   **Description**: Speak a 60-second unstructured brain dump about your active tasks before going on vacation. The app automatically structures this into a beautiful, shareable Kanban handoff board with delegated owners and timeline estimates.\n*   **Why It Matters**: Reduces the friction and anxiety of preparing for time off.\n*   **Track**: Work and Productivity\n*   **Aha Moment**: Record 30 seconds of rambling speech $\\rightarrow$ turns into an elegant, interactive Kanban board ready to share via a single URL.\n*   **3-Day Scope Cut**: Local browser storage for boards; shareable via compressed URL state payloads (no database needed).\n*   **Beat the Median**:\n    *   *Tech*: Voice transcription mapped to complex structured state.\n    *   *Design*: Ultra-clean task-board UI inspired by Linear.\n    *   *Impact*: Every office worker experiences pre-vacation handoff anxiety.\n    *   *Quality*: Solves a highly specific coordination problem elegantly.\n\n### 6. Mockup: Instant Database & CRUD API\n*   **Description**: Paste a messy JSON payload or raw text table and instantly generate an optimized database schema (Prisma/SQL), realistic seed data, and a live, testable REST mock API endpoint.\n*   **Why It Matters**: Speeds up early-stage backend architecture planning and frontend prototyping.\n*   **Track**: Developer Tools\n*   **Aha Moment**: Paste unstructured JSON $\\rightarrow$ clean, interactive entity-relationship diagram $\\rightarrow$ live mock API endpoint ready t